Martha Stewart Living Omnimedia Inc. (MSO) is a diversified media and merchandising company founded by Martha Stewart owned by Sequential Brands Group since December 4, 2015. It is organized into four business segments: Publishing, Internet, Broadcasting media platforms, and Merchandising product lines.[2] MSLO's business holdings include a variety of print publications, television and radio programming, and e-commerce websites.



