Ms. Lisa  GershGersh co-founded and served as president and COO of Oxygen Media until its 2007 acquisition by NBC Universal where she served as president of Strategic Initiatives at NBC News and interim CEO at The Weather Channel Interactive Inc. She was CEO and president at Martha Stewart Living Omnimedia from 2011 until 2013, and CEO of Goop, Inc. until 2016. She is a director of Hasbro since 2010.2017 Third QuarterAdded to: ComScore Inc. - Reston, VAComScore provides digital media analytics solutions. Revenues are $369 million.2010 Third QuarterAdded to: Hasbro Inc. - Pawtucket, RIHasbro provides children's and family leisure entertainment products. Revenues are $5 billion.















 















 


























